name: They are all going to laugh
description:
They are all going to laugh, 2022, video, 8s

I love exploring the uncanny.  A laugh can be something positive that brings us together, or it can be maniacal, a tool used to expel someone from a group.  This piece examines the maniacal nature of the laugh paired with our capability to document and propagate almost anything we desire.  See more at www.laladrona.com
